window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>He’s a notorious crime lord, a kidnapper, and an artist. </p> <p>Scarification is his outlet, and he just captured a new canvas. </p> <p>Kate refuses to surrender beneath his blade or the cruelty in his beautiful eyes. But she’s drawn to the man inside the monster. A man who makes her ache with his touch. Who owns her with his kiss. </p> <p>A man who worships her as deeply as he hurts her. </p> <p>She can run, but there’s no escape from a bond carved in scars. </p> <p>HEA with no cliffhanger. Must be listened to in order.</p>"; 
